INSERT INTO `ym_translations` VALUES ('2239', '{{class_category_file_links}}', '161', 'summary', 'en', 'Why should you study TOEFL Writing Success 4th Edition?\r\nThis book that is suitable for Upper-intermediate and Advanced test takers provides proven techniques for a higher score in such tests as TOEFL, IELTS, GRE, and GMAT. The book contains 4 writing samples by the author together with 165 writing samples of my top students, most of whom had a score between 27 and 30. The reasons why this book has been successful are as follows: \r\n1.	Using practical vocabularies and phrase that are essential for all tests.\r\n2.	Having quite a few “Introductions” and “Conclusions”\r\n3.	Offering 6 techniques, together with several samples, to complete body paragraphs.\r\n4.	Having quite a few corrected samples such that test takers’ mistakes have been crossed out and the correct responses have been offered, helping those who may have the very mistakes.\r\n5.	Several points about common mistakes of Iranian test takers.\r\n6.	Contains punctuation lessons, which is of great help to those who want to take part in the aforementioned tests.\r\n7.	Having many Integrated samples and exercises which are great to improve students\' abilities for TOEFL. \r\n8.	Teaching how to write a plan for all the 5 model questions of the Independent Task.\r\n9.	Having a rich glossary for the difficult words used in the book, which helps test takers to understand the book better and prepares them to write great essays.\r\n10.	Offering many exercises on Paraphrasing, Synthesizing, and Note-taking skills.\r\n\r\nIt is worth mentioning that writing these samples has taken much time at the beginning. However, after much practice, these very test takers managed to write decent samples in the time given for such a task. In order to become successful, you should exactly do so. If you follow the instructions written at “To the Students,” you, too, similar to many of my students, will receive a high score in the test. For more information, please visit our website www.avayeshahir.com.\r\nWish you luck. Amir Khademolmelleh. \r\n');
